{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e025f377ac","title":"中央转发北京市委镇反计划的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"abafac90b6","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":25,"articleId":"e025f377ac","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a9c279e4a7","type":"title","text":"中央转发北京市委镇反计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"e025f377ac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"278335b48b","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，区党委，各大城市市姿：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"e025f377ac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d432303bf","type":"paragraph","text":"各大城市除东北外，镇压反革命的工作，一般地说来，还未认真地严厉地大规模地实行。从现在起应当开始这样做，不能再识了。这些城市主要是北京天津青岛上海南京广州汉口重庆及各省省城，这是反革命组织的主要巢穴，必须有计划地布置侦察和速捕，在几个月内，大系几批罪大有据的反革命分子。下面是北京的镇反计划，请你们研究仿办。其中说到拟先召集区以上各级人民代表会议的代表和各天工厂大学校，民主党派，人民团体的代表开一次会，报告反革命情况及各种罪行和犯罪证据，提高大家对反革命的优恨，然后再分批执行，这是完全必要的，各地都应这样做","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"e025f377ac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8901c4aa8","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"e025f377ac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7054712997","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"e025f377ac","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":137,"end":137}}}},"__N_SSG":true}